ISLAMABAD, Oct 11 (APP): Minister of State for Information and Broadcasting Farrukh Habib on Monday expressed  grief and sorrow over the demise of former MNA Pervaiz Malik.
In a tweet, the minister payed to Allah Almighty to rest the departed soul in eternal peace and grant courage to the bereaved family to bear this loss with fortitude.
